# Dr. Syed Saquib - Personal Website

A modern, scientifically-inspired personal website showcasing Dr. Syed Saquib's expertise in chemical engineering and environmental solutions.

## About

This website features:
- Professional profile and biography
- Educational background and achievements
- Research experience and expertise
- Contact information and academic profiles
- Responsive design for all devices
- Modern animations and interactive elements

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (with animations and responsive design)
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- Font Awesome icons
- Google Fonts

## Features

- **Responsive Design**: Works perfectly on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- **Modern UI/UX**: Clean, professional design with smooth animations
- **Interactive Elements**: Hover effects, smooth scrolling, and dynamic content
- **Scientific Theme**: Molecular backgrounds and scientific color palette
- **Performance Optimized**: Fast loading with optimized assets

